result.adr_address: 83 Jervois St, Sheung Wan, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 83 Jervois St, Sheung Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Moon Thai

reviews.text: It's pretty hard to find. It's not on the street, but in the Holiday Inn Hotel on the second floor. The food is really delicious, the red curry a really big portion. The service is attentive but not penetrating. Very good.
The dishes all trended sweet so I struggled with flavor balance. Heavy on the garlic too

I would definitely recommend Moon Thai to all of you. First of all, reasonable price point with quality food and service. Especially the salad bar, it is a out of my expectation, they can even call it a semi buffet, food from there was good as well! In terms of environment, it provide outdoor and indoor area which are pretty comfy.

One of the better Thai lunch options not only in Sheung Wan but in HK. Appetizer/ salad buffet with an option for a full main course that is under $200, with a drink and dessert. In the fall and winter, the outside seating is pretty comfortable. Gets packed so best to book for lunch!
Nice spacious seatings offers each table privacy. Yummy Thai cuisine
